{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be minimalist and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureGuard Cybersecurity</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #a52a2a; /* Brownish red */\n            --text-color: #f0f0f0;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a;\n            --secondary-color: #3a3a3a;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 960px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--brand-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #e0e0e0;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        section h2 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            display: inline-block;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, var(--background-color) 70%);\n            padding: 100px 0;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border-bottom: none;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            color: #ccc;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n\n        .service-item p {\n            color: #ddd;\n        }\n\n        #contact {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 60px 0;\n        }\n\n        #contact h2 {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        #contact p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Ensure padding doesn't affect width */\n        }\n\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #8b0000; /* Darker red */\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>SecureGuard</h1>\n        <nav>\n            <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Your Digital Fortress</h2>\n            <p>Protecting your business from the ever-evolving landscape of cyber threats.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Threat Detection & Prevention</h3>\n                <p>Proactive monitoring and advanced solutions to identify and neutralize threats before they impact your operations.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Incident Response</h3>\n                <p>Rapid and effective handling of security breaches to minimize damage and restore normal operations quickly.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Vulnerability Assessment</h3>\n                <p>Comprehensive analysis of your systems to uncover weaknesses and provide actionable recommendations for improvement.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Security Consulting</h3>\n                <p>Expert guidance to develop and implement robust security strategies tailored to your business needs.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>At SecureGuard, we are a team of dedicated cybersecurity professionals committed to safeguarding your digital assets. We leverage cutting-edge technology and deep industry expertise to provide unparalleled security solutions. Our mission is to empower businesses with the confidence to operate securely in today's interconnected world.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Ready to enhance your cybersecurity posture? Contact us today.</p>\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                    <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                    <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 SecureGuard Cybersecurity. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}